creator: Beeple NV
descriptionHtml:
The XL @ work app is built for our students and our clients It is the one place to maintain an overview of all your shifts, plan some more or get additional information. It is the perfect companion to make the next shift an even greater success !

As a student:
Always an up to date overview of all your open shifts selected for you;
Easy sign up for that one perfect job;
Manage your availability;
View all additional data regarding your next shift!

As an employer:
Real time overview of all your shifts and their status;
Select your preferred employees for the next shifts;
Add (or remove) your shifts to have full control of our services!
descriptionShort: For all the temps and clients of XL Studenten Uitzendbureau.
